original_title: David Guetta - Le Grand Show (UEFA Euro 2016)
overview: With the arrival of the Euro 2016 festivities start in large pumps with a free concert organized by UEFA and TF1. David Guetta, composer of the official song for Euro 2016 will dance several hundred people at the Champ de Mars under the Eiffel Tower a few hours of the match France Romania
title: David Guetta - Le Grand Show (UEFA Euro 2016)
